  started representing Alexandria Mobile Homes, Inc. in 1990.... I didn't want the grand jury to [k]now that I had told
  Luneau and Edmonds that I would lie if subpoenaed.  I was afraid of making such an admission because I knew that it
  would make me look bad."</p>

  <p class="footnotetext"><a href="#_ednref5" name="_edn5" class="fn" id="_edn5">[iv]</a> In <span class="CITE"><i>In
  re. </i> Patricia A. King a/k/a Patricia A. Eicher,</span> 94-0686 (La. 11/30/94),
